snippet.title: Alkahest - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/3016620

Developer Push On proudly reveals Alkahest - an action-adventure RPG set in a murky medieval world where satisfying melee combat with highly interactive environments takes center stage.

Follow us on social media to stay updated:
🔹 X (Twitter): https://x.com/Alkahest_game 
🔹 Discord: https://discord.gg/wzeS52qYb9 
🔹 Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Alkahest/
🔹 Website : https://alkahestgame.com

Launch date, platforms, and all other details will be announced later. Stay tuned!
